### Hotel API Test Requests
### RESTful API endpoints following RESTful standards
### 
### Prerequisites:
### 1. Make sure the server is running (default: http://localhost:3000)
### 2. Note: Hotel endpoints are public (no authentication required)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Variables (update these with your actual values)
@hotelId = 2

###############################################
### HOTEL RESOURCE
###############################################

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId
### Get hotel details with optional search parameters
### Query params (optional): checkInDate, checkOutDate, numberOfDays, numberOfRooms, numberOfGuests
### Note: If any date-related fields are provided, all date fields are required
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId (With search parameters)
### Get hotel details with search parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId (Invalid - partial date fields)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (if date fields are provided, all are required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId (Invalid - invalid date range)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (checkOutDate must be after checkInDate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}?checkInDate=2024-12-05&checkOutDate=2024-12-01&numberOfDays=4&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId (Invalid - numberOfDays mismatch)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (numberOfDays must match date difference)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=10&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId (Invalid - hotel not found)
### Should return 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/99999
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

###############################################
### ROOMS RESOURCE
###############################################

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms
### Search available rooms for a hotel
### Query params: checkInDate, checkOutDate, numberOfDays, numberOfRooms (default: 1), numberOfGuests, page (default: 1), limit (default: 20)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms (With pagination)
### Search rooms with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms (Page 2)
### Get second page of available rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2&page=2&limit=20
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms (Invalid - missing required fields)
### Should return 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms?checkInDate=2024-12-01
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms (Invalid - invalid date range)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (checkOutDate must be after checkInDate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms?checkInDate=2024-12-05&checkOutDate=2024-12-01&numberOfDays=4&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms (Invalid - numberOfDays mismatch)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (numberOfDays must match date difference)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=10&numberOfRooms=1&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

###############################################
### ROOM AVAILABILITY RESOURCE
###############################################

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability
### Check room availability for specific rooms
### Query params: checkInDate, checkOutDate, numberOfDays, numberOfGuests, selectedRooms (JSON array)
### Note: selectedRooms can be a JSON string or array of objects with room_id and roomQuantity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfGuests=2&selectedRooms=[{"room_id":1,"roomQuantity":1}]
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability (Multiple rooms)
### Check availability for multiple rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfGuests=4&selectedRooms=[{"room_id":1,"roomQuantity":1},{"room_id":2,"roomQuantity":1}]
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability (Invalid - missing required fields)
### Should return 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-01
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability (Invalid - missing selectedRooms)
### Should return 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability (Invalid - invalid selectedRooms format)
### Should return 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfGuests=2&selectedRooms=invalid
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability (Invalid - empty selectedRooms)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (at least one room must be selected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-01&checkOutDate=2024-12-05&numberOfDays=4&numberOfGuests=2&selectedRooms=[]
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET /api/hotels/:hotelId/rooms/availability (Invalid - invalid date range)
### Should return 400 Bad Request (checkOutDate must be after checkInDate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}/rooms/availability?checkInDate=2024-12-05&checkOutDate=2024-12-01&numberOfDays=4&numberOfGuests=2&selectedRooms=[{"room_id":1,"roomQuantity":1}]
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

